description:
AIWTC is a global intelligent tourism 3.0 project which builds a global high-quality tourism consumption platform and creates a brand-new travel credit system by using technologies such as blockchain. Up until now, AIWTC has reached cooperation with dozens of government agencies around the world, such as the France Embassy in China, Consulate General of Hungary in Chongqing, and the China-CEEC (17+1) Tourism Coordination Center and so on.

AIW is a cryptographic digital rights certificate that can be circulated on the underlying chain of AIWTC. It is not only the equity certificate of the ecological participants on the AIWTC platform, but also can be used to exchange products and services on the AIWTC platform.
name: AIW Token
